It's easy to become overwhelmed
by the flow of information if we

2bbdb3a5-6e8c-4373-9311-187c10f600ae-1
00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:25.519
don't develo the skills to
navigate our way through the

2bbdb3a5-6e8c-4373-9311-187c10f600ae-2
